      • setCapturedVideoRotates

        public void setCapturedVideoRotates(boolean capturedVideoRotates)
        Sets the orientation of captured video to follow the device orientation while streaming, or to keep the orientation that was active when streaming began.
        Parameters:
        capturedVideoRotates - True for the captured video to follow the device orientation while streaming; false to keep the orientation that was active when streaming began.

      • getCapturedVideoRotates

        Gets the value of the captured video rotatation property.
